OL,3,CSnake Pass wildfires send smoke fire
OL,4,Cand wide as crews battle the blaze
OL,6,FPeople across the region woke up to
OL,7,Fthe smell of smoke this morning after
OL,8,Fa large fire broke out off Snake Pass
OL,9,Fin the Peak District.
OL,11,FFirefighters have been tackling the
OL,12,Fwildfire since around 9pm on Thursday
OL,13,Fnight (April 30), with crews from the
OL,14,FDerbyshire Fire and Rescue Service and
OL,15,Fthe Fire Operations Group (FOG)
OL,16,Fworking through the night.
OL,18,FWitnesses in Tameside reported seeing
OL,19,Fseveral fire engines heading towards
OL,20,FSnake Pass as the incident unfolded.
