OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1777838750
OL,3,CSnake Pass wildfires send smoke fire
OL,4,Cand wide as crews battle the blaze
OL,6,FThe blaze generated a significant
OL,7,Fplume of smoke, with residents in
OL,8,FOldham, Tameside, Little Hulton, and
OL,9,Feven as far as Salford reporting the
OL,10,Fsmell this morning.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for Derbyshire Fire and
OL,13,FRescue Service said: "Partners from
OL,14,Fthe Fire Operations Group are
OL,15,Fcurrently dealing with a wildfire off
OL,16,FSnake Pass in the Peak District.
OL,18,F"The fire is likely to be causing a
OL,19,Fsmoke plume in and around the Glossop
OL,20,Farea. Please keep windows and doors
OL,21,Fclosed if you can see or smell smoke."
