OL,3,CSnake Pass wildfires send smoke fire
OL,4,Cand wide as crews battle the blaze
OL,6,FSnake Pass was closed overnight as a
OL,7,Fprecaution but has since reopened,
OL,8,FFirefighters are expected to remain at
OL,9,Fthe scene throughout the day to ensure
OL,10,Fthe blaze is fully extinguished.
